    <name>Japan Dining Map - Kyoto</name>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Gion Shinbashi Nakatani</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Gion Shinbashi Nakatani</strong><br/>Kyoto / Gion<br/>Address: 59-1, Motoyoshicho, Higashiyama-ku, Kyoto-shi, Kyoto<br/>Nearest: A 5-minute walk from Gion Sijo Station (Exit 9), Keihan Line<br/>Cuisine: Japanese, Kaiseki, Washoku<br/>Reservation: Reservation request<br/>Dinner range: $$$$ JPY 20k-30k<br/>Dinner: JPY 24,200 - 24,200<br/>Lunch range: $$ JPY 5k-10k<br/>Lunch: JPY 6,600 - 2,420,014,300<br/>Child policy: Elementary school students and above are welcome.<br/>Summary: Look for the lattice paper lantern to find this kappo cuisine restaurant hidden in the back streets of Gion.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244361/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>135.77441073954105,35.005999850633515,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Hassun</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Hassun</strong><br/>Kyoto / Gion<br/>Address: 95, Sueyoshicho, Higashiyama-ku, Kyoto-shi, Kyoto<br/>Nearest: ; ; A 5-minute walk from Gion-shijo Station (Keihan Main Line); ; ; A 8-minute walk from Kawaramachi Station (Hankyu Kyoto Line)<br/>Cuisine: Japanese, Kaiseki, Washoku<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$$$ JPY 20k-30k<br/>Dinner: JPY 22,000 - 22,000<br/>Lunch range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Lunch: JPY 11,000 - 11,000<br/>Child policy: Children are welcome from the age of 13, but only in the tatami room<br/>Summary: The essence of 2-star Kyoto cuisine in Gion, with each ingredient’s natural flavor captured using traditional cooking techniques.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244990/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>135.77377539128065,35.00486675247475,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>KOBE BEEF STEAK Mouriya Gion</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>KOBE BEEF STEAK Mouriya Gion</strong><br/>Kyoto / Gion<br/>Address: Gion Moriya Building, 7-1 , Yamatooji-dori Shijo-sagaru Yamatocho, Higashiyama-ku, Kyoto-shi, Kyoto<br/>Nearest: A 1-minute walk from Gion Shijo Station, KH39 Exit 6, Keihan Line<br/>Cuisine: Steak, Teppanyaki<br/>Reservation: Reservation request<br/>Dinner range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Dinner: JPY 13,700 - 38,900<br/>Lunch range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Lunch: JPY 10,200 - 35,400<br/>Child policy: Child age 10+<br/>Summary: Enjoy real Kobe beef at this Gion steakhouse in Kyoto.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244381/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>135.7727682715757,35.00336111626586,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Kenninji Gion Maruyama</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Kenninji Gion Maruyama</strong><br/>Kyoto / Gion<br/>Address: 566-16, Komatsucho, Higashiyama-ku, Kyoto-shi, Kyoto<br/>Nearest: A 15-minutes walk from Gion-Shijo Station on the Keihan Main Line<br/>Cuisine: Japanese, Kaiseki, Washoku<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$$$$ JPY 30k+<br/>Dinner: JPY 37,950 - 88,550<br/>Lunch range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Lunch: JPY 18,975 - 88,550<br/>Child policy: Child age 0+<br/>Summary: A 2-star Japanese restaurant opened near Kennin-ji Temple in Kyoto that celebrates each season with special dishes and decorations.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/245198/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>135.77457301318645,34.99874813574185,0</coordinates>
