    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Ryō-shō</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Ryō-shō</strong><br/>Kyoto / Gion<br/>Address: 570-166, Gionmachi Minamigawa, Higashiyama-ku, Kyoto-shi, Kyoto<br/>Nearest: 8 minutes walk from Gion-Shijo Station<br/>Cuisine: Japanese, Kaiseki, Washoku<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$$$$ JPY 30k+<br/>Dinner: JPY 44,000 - 44,000<br/>Lunch range: $$$$ JPY 20k+<br/>Lunch: JPY 44,000 - 44,000<br/>Child policy: Child age 13+<br/>Summary: A 2-star Japanese restaurant in Gion helmed by a master of Kyoto cuisine, offering unforgettable dishes and dining experiences in an extraordinary setting.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/245339/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>135.77585393588802,35.002370515613606,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>BENOIT Kyoto</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>BENOIT Kyoto</strong><br/>Kyoto / Kyoto<br/>Address: The Hotel Seiryu Kyoto Kiyomizu, 2-204-2, Kiyomizu, Higashiyama-ku, Kyoto-shi, Kyoto<br/>Nearest: Approximately 15-minute taxi ride from Kyoto Station (JR Tokaido Main Line (Kyoto Line) (Kyoto - Osaka), JR Tokaido Main Line (Biwako Line) (Maibara - Kyoto); A 20-minute walk from Gion-shijo Station and Kiyomizu-gojo Station (Keihan Main Line); Approximately 5-minute walk from the Kiyomizu-michi bus stop of the Kyoto City Bus<br/>Cuisine: French<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$ Under JPY 10k<br/>Dinner: JPY 8,800 - 12,430<br/>Lunch range: $$ JPY 5k-10k<br/>Lunch: JPY 6,600 - 9,680<br/>Child policy: Children 7 years old and older are welcome to visit<br/>Summary: A restaurant in the historic city of Kyoto imbued with the spirit and flavors of a beloved Paris bistro.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244965/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>135.779685,34.997335,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Dominique Bouchet Kyoto Le RESTAURANT</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Dominique Bouchet Kyoto Le RESTAURANT</strong><br/>Kyoto / Kyoto<br/>Address: 3F, 1, Awataguchi Kachocho, Higashiyama-ku, Kyoto-shi, Kyoto<br/>Nearest: A 2-minute walk from Keage Station (Kyoto City Subway Tozai Line)<br/>Cuisine: French<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$$$ JPY 20k-30k<br/>Dinner: JPY 20,000 - 30,000<br/>Lunch range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Lunch: JPY 10,000 - 18,000<br/>Child policy: Reservations for junior high students and older are accepted in the main dining.<br/>Summary: Have an unforgettable dining experience enjoying Chef Bouchet’s luxurious French cuisine and spectacular panoramic views of Kyoto from the Westin Miyako location.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244791/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>135.78739,35.008531,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Dominique Bouchet Kyoto Le Teppanyaki</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Dominique Bouchet Kyoto Le Teppanyaki</strong><br/>Kyoto / Kyoto<br/>Address: 3F, 1, Awataguchi Kachocho, Higashiyama-ku, Kyoto-shi, Kyoto<br/>Nearest: A 2-minute walk from Keage Station (Kyoto City Subway Tozai Line)<br/>Cuisine: Steak, Teppanyaki<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$$$ JPY 20k-30k<br/>Dinner: JPY 20,000 - 40,000<br/>Lunch range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Lunch: JPY 10,000 - 33,000<br/>Child policy: Child age 0+<br/>Summary: French cuisine master Dominique Bouchet’s first teppanyaki restaurant serves up delicious teppanyaki made from the best Japanese ingredients with a French twist.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244766/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>135.78739,35.008531,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Harise</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Harise</strong><br/>Kyoto / Kyoto<br/>Address: 294 Fukuromachi, Daikokucho-dori Gojo-sagaru, Higashiyama-ku, Kyoto-shi, Kyoto<br/>Nearest: Keihan Main Line &quot;Kiyomizu Gojyo&quot;  5-minute walk<br/>Cuisine: Japanese, Kaiseki, Washoku<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Dinner: JPY 13,950 - 31,625<br/>Lunch range: $$ JPY 5k-10k<br/>Lunch: JPY 6,050 - 10,120<br/>Summary: A beloved Kyoto institution that has been in business for over 350 years, famous for its eccentric local cuisine, especially its variety of dishes incorporating soups, and for its dedication in catering to each customer’s preferences.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244008/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>135.77085882425308,34.99471677766799,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Jikishinbou Saiki</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Jikishinbou Saiki</strong><br/>Kyoto / Kyoto<br/>Address: 443-1, Kamibentencho, Higashiyama-ku, Kyoto-shi, Kyoto<br/>Nearest: 15 minute walk from Gion-Shijo station(Keihan Main Line)<br/>Cuisine: Japanese, Kaiseki, Washoku<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Dinner: JPY 16,500 - 33,000<br/>Lunch range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Lunch: JPY 15,000 - 15,000<br/>Child policy: Junior high school students and above are welcome<br/>Summary: Guests have been enjoying the traditional, classic atmosphere at this Kyoto establishment for over 90 years. Located near Yasaka Shrine and Kiyomizu-dera, the chef’s broth and rice are not to be missed.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244081/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>135.77807195484638,35.001470384846634,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Kodaiji Jugyuan</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Kodaiji Jugyuan</strong><br/>Kyoto / Kyoto<br/>Address: 353 Masuya-cho, Kodai-ji, Higashiyama-ku, Kyoto-shi, Kyoto<br/>Nearest: A 20-minute walk from Gion-Shijo Station, Exit 6 (Keihan Main Line)<br/>Cuisine: Japanese, Kaiseki, Washoku<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$$$ JPY 20k-30k<br/>Dinner: JPY 25,300 - 63,250<br/>Lunch range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Lunch: JPY 18,975 - 18,975<br/>Child policy: Children are welcome and children menu is available<br/>Summary: A 1 star ryotei restaurant, overlooking the famous garden from the 110-year-old sukiya building, where guests can enjoy delicious traditional Kyoto cuisine.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244694/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>135.7814797013998,34.99859323506716,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Nichigetsubo Tan</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Nichigetsubo Tan</strong><br/>Kyoto / Kyoto<br/>Address: 10-33, Kankiji cho, Shimogyo-ku, Kyoto-shi, Kyoto<br/>Nearest: A 15-minute walk from Gion-shijo Station (Keihan Main Line)<br/>Cuisine: Japanese, Kaiseki, Washoku<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$$$ JPY 20k-30k<br/>Dinner: JPY 23,000 - 23,000<br/>Lunch range: $$$$ JPY 20k+<br/>Lunch: JPY 23,000 - 23,000<br/>Child policy: Children of any age are welcome to visit the restaurant, but we do not have children&#x27;s chairs (Children&#x27;s tableware is available)<br/>Summary: A Japanese restaurant in Machiya in Kyoto that aims to present a new world to its guests with carefully selected dishes.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244734/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>135.74443638324738,34.98891026235291,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Shorenin Monzeki-mae Tsukioka</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Shorenin Monzeki-mae Tsukioka</strong><br/>Kyoto / Kyoto<br/>Address: 16-2, Awataguchi Sanjobocho, Higashiyama-ku, Kyoto-shi, Kyoto<br/>Nearest: A 5-minutes walk from Higashiyama Station on the Kyoto City Subway<br/>Cuisine: Japanese, Kaiseki, Washoku<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$$$$ JPY 30k+<br/>Dinner: JPY 30,000 - 30,000<br/>Lunch range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Lunch: JPY 15,000 - 15,000<br/>Child policy: Children are welcome, if they can enjoy the same menu as adults<br/>Summary: Chef Tsukioka truly embodies the Japanese concept of ‘chiso’, entertaining his guests whilst serving them a banquet created from the very finest ingredients that he meticulously sources from all over Japan.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/245258/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>135.78251905739307,35.008057018060626,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
